<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - Celestial Gatherings</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron&family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Platypi:ital,wght@0,300..800;1,300..800&display=swap">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles-core.css">

</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/header') %>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<div class="container">
    <h1 style="text-align: center;">Welcome to Celestial Gatherings</h1>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <p class="intro-text" style="text-align: center;">
        Join us for exciting space-themed events and meetups!
    </p>

    <hr class="icon">

    <section>
        <h2>Why Join Us?</h2>
        <p class="intro-text">
            Celestial Gatherings brings together space enthusiasts from all walks of life to explore the wonders of the universe.
            Whether you're an amateur astronomer, a seasoned stargazer, or just curious about the night sky, there's something for everyone!
        </p>
    </section>

    <hr class="icon">

    <h2>Space Images</h2>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <img src="/images/main_1.jpg" alt="Space from Earth" class="img-fluid fixed-size">
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <img src="/images/main_2.jpg" alt="Astronaut in Space" class="img-fluid fixed-size">
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <img src="/images/main_3.jpg" alt="Space" class="img-fluid fixed-size">
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <img src="/images/main_4.jpg" alt="Space" class="img-fluid fixed-size">
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="icon">

    <section>
        <h2>Space Facts</h2>
        <ul class="normal-text">
            <li>Space is completely silent. There is no atmosphere to carry sound.</li>
            <li>One day on Venus is longer than one year on Earth. It takes Venus about 243 Earth days to rotate once on its axis.</li>
            <li>Jupiter has the shortest day of all the planets, completing a rotation on its axis in just under 10 hours.</li>
            <li>There are more stars in the universe than grains of sand on all the Earth's beaches combined.</li>
            <li>The footprints left by astronauts on the moon are likely to last millions of years, with no wind or water to erode them.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <hr class="icon">

    <section>
        <h2>Testimonials</h2>
        <div class="testimonial">
            <p class="testimonial-text">"Celestial Gatherings has rekindled my love for astronomy. Every event is well-organized and a lot of fun!"</p>
            <div class="testimonial-name">- Jane Doe</div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
            <p class="testimonial-text">"I've learned so much and met so many great people through this group. Highly recommend joining!"</p>
            <div class="testimonial-name">- John Doe</div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>

